'''Notho''', also known as '''Nothoiin''', was the native language of the [[Nothoiin (species)/Legends|Nothoiin]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Nothoiin/Legends|Nothoiin]].

It was a hand language developed by the hunters in the local plains.

Most Nothoiins were fluent and literate in both Notho and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Galactic Basic Standard]].

